trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers for <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider"></xref>.
These values are used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TransformPattern>.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider.IsReadOnly*> property.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.
To be added.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider.LargeChange*> property.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.
To be added.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider.Maximum*> property.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.
To be added.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider.Minimum*> property.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.
To be added.
Identifies this pattern as a <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern"></xref>.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.

The pattern [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] is passed to methods such as <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A> to specify the pattern to return.
To be added.

This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.
To be added.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider.Value*> property.
This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.RangeValuePattern>.
To be added.
